    body: 'Aggregates every fund’s latest filing per security and layers on multi-factor filters, a bullish-vs-bearish sentiment split, and savable presets — so conviction scores never get inflated by put-heavy positions.',
    icon: 'M3 3v18h18 M7 14l4-4 3 3 5-6',
    tags: ['Multi-factor filters', 'Sentiment split', 'Savable presets'],
  },
  {
